- 32 passing tests covering: base premiums by item type, processing fee, block discount for 3 alike components, cursed/high-enchantment item surcharges, loyalty/first-insurance/follow-up policy modifiers, multi-item modifier scoping, premium rounding (up, in MHPCO favor), claim payouts with per-damage deductibles, high-enchantment 50% reimbursement clause, cap exhaustion across successive claims, multiple items of the same type, and error handling for unknown item types / out-of-policy damages / negative amounts
- CLI at `src/cli.ts` reads JSON from stdin, writes JSON to stdout, exits non-zero on errors
